---
// src/components/PainPoints.astro
---
<section class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-semibold text-dark-gray text-center mb-16">
      ¿Tu consulta te drena la energía?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <!-- Tarjeta 1: El Caos de la Agenda -->
      <div class="bg-light-gray p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <!-- Icono: Calendario desordenado (Placeholder) -->
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 text-persian-green-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0h18M-4.5 12.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark-gray mb-2">El vaivén de mensajes</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-dark-gray/80">
          Pierdes horas cada semana coordinando citas por WhatsApp y email, tiempo que podrías dedicar a tus pacientes o a ti misma.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjeta 2: El Estrés del Cobro -->
      <div class="bg-light-gray p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <!-- Icono: Moneda con cara triste (Placeholder) -->
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 text-persian-green-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 11.21 12.77 11 12 11s-1.536.21-2.121.782c-1.172.879-1.172 2.303 0 3.182z" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark-gray mb-2">Conversaciones incómodas</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-dark-gray/80">
          Te sientes incómoda recordando pagos o gestionando cancelaciones, afectando la relación terapéutica.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjeta 3: La Frustración del Marketing -->
      <div class="bg-light-gray p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <!-- Icono: Megáfono tachado (Placeholder) -->
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 text-persian-green-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6h9.75M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 10-3 0M3.75 6H7.5m3 12h9.75m-9.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5m9-6h3.75m-3.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-9.75 0h9.75" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark-gray mb-2">Sentirte "invisible"</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-dark-gray/80">
          Sabes que puedes ayudar a más personas, pero no tienes tiempo ni energía para "venderte" en redes sociales.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
